headline: UPS Releases 3Q 2025 Earnings
summary: ATLANTA, October 28, 2025--UPS (NYSE:UPS) today announced third-quarter 2025 consolidated revenues of $21.4 billion. Consolidated operating profit was $1.8 billion; $2.1 billion on a non-GAAP adjusted basis. Diluted earnings per share were $1.55 for the quarter; non-GAAP adjusted diluted earnings per share were $1.74.

headline: PayPal and UPS help lead US stocks to more records
summary: The U.S. stock market pushed further into record heights  on Tuesday.  The Dow Jones Industrial Average rose 161 points, or 0.3%, and the Nasdaq composite climbed 0.8%.  Moves were also relatively modest in the bond market as Wall Street waits for a few events that could shake things up.
